data.value: <?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?> <DeviceConfiguration xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema"> <SyncPatterns> <SyncPattern> <Identifier>itunes-style</Identifier> <Name>Artist\Album\Track</Name> <Pattern>%ARTIST%\%ALBUM%\%TRACKNUMSPACE%%NAME%</Pattern> <Description>This pattern places the tracks the same way iTunes places tracks in a managed iTunes music folder. Files are organized by Album Artist\Album\DiscNumber-TrackNumber Name.</Description> <CompilationsPattern>Compilations\%ALBUM%\%DISCNUMDASH%%TRACKNUMSPACE%%NAME%</CompilationsPattern> </SyncPattern> <SyncPattern> <Identifier>one-folder</Identifier> <Name>Artist - Album\Track</Name> <Pattern>%ARTIST% - %ALBUM%\%TRACKNUMSPACE%%NAME%</Pattern> <Description>This pattern organizes the tracks in folders named by Artist and album. Files are organized like this: Artist - Album\TrackNumber Name.</Description> <CompilationsPattern>%ALBUM%\%TRACKNUMSPACE%%NAME%</CompilationsPattern> </SyncPattern> <SyncPattern> <Identifier>one-folder-disc</Identifier> <Name>Artist - Album\Track (with disc number)</Name> <Pattern>%ARTIST% - %ALBUM%\%DISCNUMDASH%%TRACKNUMSPACE%%NAME%</Pattern> <Description>This pattern organizes the tracks in folders named by Artist and album. Files are organized like this: Artist - Album\DiscNumber-TrackNumber Name.</Description> <CompilationsPattern>%ALBUM%\%DISCNUMDASH%%TRACKNUMSPACE%%NAME%</CompilationsPattern> </SyncPattern> <SyncPattern> <Identifier>one-folder-albumartist</Identifier> <Name>Album Artist - Album\Track</Name> <Pattern>%ALBUMARTIST% - %ALBUM%\%TRACKNUMSPACE%%NAME%</Pattern> <Description>This pattern organizes the tracks in folders named by Album Artist and album. Files are organized like this: Album Artist - Album\TrackNumber Name.</Description> <CompilationsPattern>%ALBUMARTIST%\%TRACKNUMSPACE%%NAME%</CompilationsPattern> </SyncPattern> <SyncPattern> <Identifier>one-folder-disc-albumartist</Identifier> <Name>Album Artist - Album\Track (with disc number)</Name> <Pattern>%ALBUMARTIST% - %ALBUM%\%DISCNUMDASH%%TRACKNUMSPACE%%NAME%</Pattern> <Description>This pattern organizes the tracks in folders named by Album Artist and album. Files are organized like this: Album Artist - Album\DiscNumber-TrackNumber Name.</Description> <CompilationsPattern>%ALBUMARTIST%\%DISCNUMDASH%%TRACKNUMSPACE%%NAME%</CompilationsPattern> </SyncPattern> <SyncPattern> <Identifier>artistonly</Identifier> <Name>Artist\Track</Name> <Pattern>%ARTIST%\%TRACKNUMSPACE%%NAME%</Pattern> <Description>This pattern organizes the tracks in folders named by Artist only. Files are organized like this: Artist\TrackNumber Name.</Description> <CompilationsPattern>%ALBUMARTIST%\%TRACKNUMSPACE%%NAME%</CompilationsPattern> </SyncPattern> <SyncPattern> <Identifier>artistonly-disc</Identifier> <Name>Artist\Track (with disc number)</Name> <Pattern>%ARTIST%\%DISCNUMDASH%%TRACKNUMSPACE%%NAME%</Pattern> <Description>This pattern organizes the tracks in folders named by Artist only (including disc number). Files are organized like this: Artist\DiscNumber-TrackNumber Name.</Description> <CompilationsPattern>%ARTIST%\%DISCNUMDASH%%TRACKNUMSPACE%%NAME%</CompilationsPattern> </SyncPattern> <SyncPattern> <Identifier>flat</Identifier> <Name>Artist - Track</Name> <Pattern>%ARTIST% - %NAME%</Pattern> <Description>This pattern organizes all tracks in the root media folder of the device. All tracks from all artists are in one folder and names like this: Artist - Name.</Description> <CompilationsPattern /> </SyncPattern> </SyncPatterns> <Devices> <Device> <Name>Example Configuration</Name> <MediaRoot>Music</MediaRoot> <SyncPattern>itunes-style</SyncPattern> <RecognizePattern>AnUniqueFileForMyDevice.notpod</RecognizePattern> <Playlist /> <InitialTracks /> </Device> </Devices> </DeviceConfiguration>

data.name: logging
data.value:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?> <log4net> <appender name="LogFile" type="log4net.Appender.FileAppender"> <file value="notpod.log" /> <appendToFile value="true" />
<layout type="log4net.Layout.PatternLayout"> <conversionPattern value="%5level [%thread] (%logger:%line) - %message%newline" /> </layout> </appender>
<root> <level value="INFO" /> <appender-ref ref="LogFile" /> </root> </log4net>
